      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Good overview: only one thing I&#39;d disagree with -- while for incremental/streaming, SAX and Stax are good, standard API sufficient, for DOM this is not the case (IMO): there are valid reasons for Java-specific takes like XOM, JDOM and DOM4J: language-agnostic DOM is pretty cumbersome to use."
